title: Healthcare startup in radiology is looking for a Senior Deep Learning Team Lead and a Senior Deep Learning Expert
description:
Hello PyTorch community,

https://contextflow.com/, a startup developing artificial intelligence-based software applications to support radiologists during their clinical routine, is looking for a:

Senior Deep Learning Team Lead
https://contextflow.com/jobs/senior-deep-learning-team-lead/

Senior Deep Learning Expert
https://contextflow.com/jobs/senior-deep-learning-expert/

If you you are interested send an email to jobs@contextflow.com.

Kind regards
Michael

title: Freelancers required for deep learning
description: For the implementation of unsupervised segmentation of my image data, I am looking for freelancers support. Please contact me (blue69moon@protonmail.com) if you are interested in freelancing with me through freelancing platform like Fiverr or Upwork. Thank you.
